As we discussed we are planning to do an information system for banking operations.For that we need to figureout functional and non functional requirements first.

functional requirements
•	The bank must process the request of a user by verifying the details of customer, like, whether that is a valid account. If user initiate to transfer found check if the account has enough money.
•	Bank able to update the current balance after each transaction.
•	Interest rate should be updated automatically
•	A valid user can check his balance and perform money transactions
•	User can change his login password
Nonfunctional requirements
•	Bank can add or remove a customer
•	User must log in to their account by a username and password for security
•	Bank can suspend any account for a period
•	The service must be available at any time


